Events.Text: I want to reserve a room at the Hilton Hotel from May 2nd to 23rd, please
You remember that your friend recommended the Shadyside Inn. Tell the assistant you've changed your mind and want to stay at Shadyside Inn. [instruction 1 of 5]

Scenario.UserTask: You want to reserve a room at the Hilton Hotel from May 2nd to 23rd. Your name is Ben. Please do not make a custom request, and it is ok if no room is available - just say goodbye in this case.
